    <desc>Fun set of flowy trails and not technical. Sometimes trails are marked as closed because of rain but this route is the least muddy way through.  You can spend more time in here riding on additional trails. Very well market. Most are doable on a cross bike. The loop I recommend is Brainbuster, Rabbit Run, Red Pine Loop, Razor’s Run, The Shocker, The Maples, Devil’s Elbow, The Express and then back up Rabbit Run.  Above is the gps route for this. </desc>
